SEC. 3.

Rehabilitation Council.

- There is hereby created a Bacolor Rehabilitation Council which shall composed of the following:

The Regional Director of the National Economic and Development Authority (NEDA)-Regional Office 3, as chairperson;

The Mayor of Bacolor, Pampanga, as vice-chairperson;

The Governor of Pampanga, as member;

The President of the Association of Barangay Captains (ABC) of Bacolor, Pampanga, as member;

The Regional Director of the Department of Public Works and Highways (DPWH)-Regional Office 3, as member;

The Regional Director of the Department of Agriculture (DA)-Regional Office 3, as member;

The Regional Director of the Department of Trade and Industry (DTI)-Regional Office 3, as member;

The Regional Director of the Department of Education (DepEd)-Regional Office 3, as member;

The Regional Director of the Department of Health (DOH)-Regional Office 3, as member;

The Representative of the 3rd District of Pampanga or his authorized representative, as member;

The President of the Chamber of Commerce and Industries of Pampanga, as member;

A representative from a Bacolor-based nongovernment organization (NGO), as member; and
